{
  "id": "6a1e57cad3a0687a0a16789a",
  "title": "嘘をつけ系の言葉",
  "created": 1780373453,
  "updated": 1780373859,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1e57cad3a0687a0a16789a",
      "text": "嘘をつけ系の言葉",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373453,
      "updated": 1780373453
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e580100000000006cb796",
      "text": "嘘をつけ系の言葉を集めたい[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373505,
      "updated": 1780373514
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e57cc00000000006cb793",
      "text": " 相手が嘘を言っているであろう時に「嘘をつけ」という命令形の言い回しをする",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373453,
      "updated": 1780373506
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e57f000000000006cb795",
      "text": "\tこれと同じような用法の言葉を集めたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373489,
      "updated": 1780373500
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e57d400000000006cb794",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373461,
      "updated": 1780373461
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e583100000000006cb79d",
      "text": "不思議な言い回しだと思っていたが、コトバンクに上手い説明が載ってるのをみて納得した",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373553,
      "updated": 1780373611
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e584b00000000006cb79f",
      "text": " [https://kotobank.jp/word/嘘を吐け-201068 嘘を吐け | コトバンク]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373579,
      "updated": 1780373634
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e588400000000006cb7a0",
      "text": "  > うそをつくならつけ、こちらにはわかっているぞという気持で、相手の言ったことが本当でないのをとがめて言う表現。うそを言うな。うそを言え。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373636,
      "updated": 1780373657
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e583100000000006cb79e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373553,
      "updated": 1780373553
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e580b00000000006cb797",
      "text": "嘘をつけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373516,
      "updated": 1780373520
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e581000000000006cb799",
      "text": "\t嘘つけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373520,
      "updated": 1780373523
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e581200000000006cb79a",
      "text": "ほざけ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373523,
      "updated": 1780373529
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e581800000000006cb79b",
      "text": "\tほざいてろ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373529,
      "updated": 1780373532
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e581d00000000006cb79c",
      "text": " 言ってろ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373534,
      "updated": 1780373542
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e594900000000006cb7a2",
      "text": "やれるものならやってみろ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373834,
      "updated": 1780373841
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e595000000000006cb7a3",
      "text": "\tやってみろ単体で（この意味で）用いる事はあるのだろうか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373841,
      "updated": 1780373859
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1e580b00000000006cb798",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780373516,
      "updated": 1780373516
    }
  ]
}